NAME

  dtol - translates DOS formatted text files into Linux formatted text files

SYNOPSIS

  dtol (flags)

DESCRIPTION

  dtol is designed to translate a DOS formatted text file into a Linux formatted
  text file. dtol will translate each carriage return + line feed end of line
  character sequence to a line feed end of line character sequence.

FLAGS

  -h  display the flags that can be interpreted by dtol
  -i  input file
  -o  output file
  -v  display version
  -s  report statistics
  -w  write over mode (input file will be overwritten as output)

  Standard input and output are assumed if no file names were specified.

